I will bear to provide salvation.

00:47:12.579 --> 00:47:14.621
And with and in the name of Yahowah,

00:47:15.521 --> 00:47:17.163
I will be summoned and called.

00:47:17.664 --> 00:47:19.385
I will be read aloud and welcomed

00:47:20.322 --> 00:47:21.802
as I am appointed to the Miqra'ey.

00:47:25.302 --> 00:47:28.344
My promise and offering to Yahowah,

00:47:29.003 --> 00:47:30.264
I will complete.

00:47:31.304 --> 00:47:33.525
Totally satisfying and fulfilling the

00:47:33.545 --> 00:47:33.965
purpose.

00:47:35.045 --> 00:47:37.467
Conspicuously and in all earnestness,

00:47:38.067 --> 00:47:39.867
as a corresponding counterpart,

00:47:40.427 --> 00:47:42.588
publicly before all of his people,

00:47:46.280 --> 00:47:48.942
and so exceedingly rare and influential,

00:47:49.481 --> 00:47:50.862
highly valued and honored,

00:47:51.202 --> 00:47:53.063
treasured and respected for their

00:47:53.103 --> 00:47:54.364
intrinsic worth.

00:47:55.144 --> 00:47:58.748
In the eyes of Yahowah is the death

00:47:58.788 --> 00:48:02.389
of the physical bodies of his Chesed,

00:48:03.530 --> 00:48:08.072
his reliable and devoted ones.

00:48:08.092 --> 00:48:10.574
Emphasizing and requesting this,

00:48:11.963 --> 00:48:15.565
earnestly seeking this opportunity that I

00:48:15.626 --> 00:48:16.606
know will occur.

00:48:17.146 --> 00:48:19.208
Yahowah, indeed, it is true.

00:48:20.250 --> 00:48:21.891
I am your coworker.

00:48:22.632 --> 00:48:24.213
I am your servant.

00:48:25.333 --> 00:48:27.896
I am the son of your ‘Amah,

00:48:29.016 --> 00:48:29.916
productive mother.

00:48:31.778 --> 00:48:34.280
You have responded to open and release

00:48:34.320 --> 00:48:36.402
that which pertains to my bonds,

00:48:36.882 --> 00:48:40.126
freeing me from losing self-control.

00:48:41.442 --> 00:48:43.182
through disciplined instruction,

00:48:46.085 --> 00:48:47.447
on your behalf and for you,

00:48:49.307 --> 00:48:53.351
I will absolutely become the sacrificial

00:48:53.431 --> 00:48:53.791
offering.

00:48:55.452 --> 00:48:58.275
Thankful for the opportunity while

00:48:58.315 --> 00:48:59.876
conveying appreciation.

00:49:01.617 --> 00:49:02.998
And in the name of Yahowah,

00:49:03.579 --> 00:49:05.000
I will be summoned and I will be

00:49:05.079 --> 00:49:05.641
read aloud,

00:49:05.701 --> 00:49:08.663
called out and welcomed as I have always

00:49:08.702 --> 00:49:10.704
been appointed to the Miqra'ey.

00:49:12.981 --> 00:49:13.121
Well,

00:49:13.161 --> 00:49:16.262
my binding promise and offering to Yahowah

00:49:17.382 --> 00:49:20.222
is that I will honor and complete totally

00:49:20.262 --> 00:49:23.603
satisfying and fulfilling emphatically and

00:49:23.664 --> 00:49:26.623
conspicuously as a corresponding

00:49:26.664 --> 00:49:29.324
counterpart publicly in front of all of

00:49:29.364 --> 00:49:33.846
his people within the courtyard and city

00:49:35.146 --> 00:49:39.527
beside the walls of the house of Yahowah

00:49:40.987 --> 00:49:41.788
in your midst.

00:49:45.568 --> 00:49:47.989
SOURCE OF INSTRUCTION ON RECONCILIATION.

00:49:49.510 --> 00:49:52.130
HALLELUJAH.

00:49:52.190 --> 00:49:52.550
SHINE.

00:49:53.472 --> 00:49:54.251
YAHWEH'S LIGHT.

00:49:57.132 --> 00:49:58.454
Mizmowr SONG, PSALM.

00:50:00.695 --> 00:50:04.235
ONE SIXTEEN FROM BEGINNING TO END.

00:50:06.818 --> 00:50:10.219
MY LIFE'S WORK IS DONE.

00:50:11.380 --> 00:50:12.119
IT IS COMPLETE.

00:50:13.353 --> 00:50:17.074
at least in this phase.

00:50:17.135 --> 00:50:19.175
Thank you for listening.

00:50:19.215 --> 00:50:23.157
Good evening.

00:50:23.237 --> 00:50:24.757
Hey there, thanks for tuning in.

00:50:24.777 --> 00:50:25.597
That was Fetch.

00:50:25.657 --> 00:50:26.157
Gotta run now.

00:50:26.177 --> 00:50:27.097
Catch y'all on our next podcast.